<section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl scroll-mt-20 px-6 py-16">
	<p class="section-label mb-6">About Me</p>
	<div class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
		<p>
			I'm an Operations Engineer at <span class="text-fg">TrackMan</span> with a
			Computer Science &amp; Engineering background from <span class="text-fg"
				>Ohio State</span
			>. My work sits at the intersection of software, field systems, radar
			technology, monitoring, and automation. 

		</p>
		<br />
		<p>
		Before TrackMan, I worked with <span class="text-fg"
				>PGA TOUR ShotLink</span>, supporting tournament technology,
			field systems, networking, and operational tooling in live production environments. 
			I like building practical systems that make technical operations easier — dashboards,
			scripts, alerting workflows, data pipelines, calibration tools, and physical-device workflows.
		</p>

	</div>

	{/* Small inline experience logos, shown in full brand color on a
	    transparent background. Files live in public/images/logos/. */}
	<div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-4">
		<span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-faint">
			Experience
		</span>
		<img
			src="/images/logos/trackman.png"
			alt="TrackMan"
			class="h-12 w-auto transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-105"
			loading="lazy"
			decoding="async"
		/>
		<img
			src="/images/logos/pga-tour.png"
			alt="PGA TOUR"
			class="h-12 w-auto transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-105"
			loading="lazy"
			decoding="async"
		/>
	</div>
</section>
